      "audioText": "看到黑影就立刻逃跑，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 55.61,
      "endTime": 56.13,
      "audioText": "不用细究，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 56.13,
      "endTime": 57.03,
      "audioText": "那是不是野兽？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 57.09,
      "endTime": 58.37,
      "audioText": "这是大脑为了节省力气，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 58.37,
      "endTime": 59.935,
      "audioText": "会刻意剔除琐碎信息，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "endTime": 62.26,
      "audioText": "只用自己熟悉的经验去判断事情。"
    },
    {
